<https://dataout.org/ontology#courtDocumentNumber> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Used to indicate a number of a court document assigned by court. It is not necessarily a unique identifier. To indicate unique identifiers, use uniqueCourtDocumentID."@en .
