# 
# https://dataout.org/ontology#monitoringRecordNumber
<https://dataout.org/ontology#monitoringRecordNumber> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://dataout.org/ontology#monitoringRecordNumber> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subPropertyOf> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> .
<https://dataout.org/ontology#monitoringRecordNumber> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://dataout.org/ontology#MonitoringRecord> .
<https://dataout.org/ontology#monitoringRecordNumber> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Literal> .
<https://dataout.org/ontology#monitoringRecordNumber> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A unique identifier assigned to a monitoring record within the Dataout monitoring system."@en .
<https://dataout.org/ontology#monitoringRecordNumber> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "monitoring record number"@en .
